label: FINANCIALINSTITUTIONNAME
description: This field stores the name of the external financial institution.

label: PRIMARYACCOUNTHOLDERNAME
description: This field stores the primary name on the account held at the external financial institution.

label: NUMBER
description: This field stores the account number of the account held at the external financial institution.

label: ACCTTYPE
description: This field stores the type of account held at the external financial institution.

label: RT
description: This field stores the external financial institution's routing number.

label: STATUS
description: This field stores the current status.

label: CREATIONDATE
description: This field stores the date the External Account record was created.

label: PRENOTESENTDATE
description: This field stores the date the system sent the prenote or the micro transaction amount to the external financial institution.

label: EXPIRATIONDATE
description: This field stores the date when the member deletes the external financial institution.

label: RECORDCHANGEDATE
description: The system stores the system date in this field when you create, change, or save the External Account record. Sometimes the system updates this field because the record was saved, even though there may not be any actual changes in the record.

label: LOCATOR
description: This field stores a unique number within each member account that can be used as a unique identification of this record.
